as required.

\subparagraph{Function Space Path} The induction hypothesis permits the
assumption that $\login{\mappath{Q_0}{p_0}}{\typemap{\typeQ}{\typeP}}{t}$ and
$\mappath{Q_1}{p_1} \le_{\typemap{\typeQ}{\typeP}} \mappath{Q_0}{p_0}$ so that
