$\login{p_1}{\typeP}{\newapply{t}{b}}$ and hence by induction that
$\login{p_0}{\typeP}{\newapply{t}{b}}$; this is immediate since
$\login{\newpath{b}{p_0}}{\typedelta\typeP}{t}$.

