induction that $\login{p_0}{\typeP_j[\typerec{}{P}{\typeP}/\vec{P}]}{\rep{t}}$;
this is immediate since by assumption
$\login{\abspath{p_0}}{\typerec{j}{P}{\typeP}}{t}$.
